                <note rend="inline" type="source">No. 3.</note>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Jay</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Fish</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1870-08-08">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">August 8, 1870.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Fish,</hi>
                    <hi rend="italic">Secretary, Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Austria declines alliance proffered by France. War preparations and
                    fortifications continue, but only as precautionary and for defense.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JAY.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
